Foud this for an older version.

Freeware Mac and DRM remover for iTunes files.
Requiem 1.8.10 for Mac supports iTunes versions 8.1.1 files
Do NOT upgrade to iTunes 8.2 or higher. 
Requiem does not remove DRM from files with rental licenses.

For more information, see http://hymn-project.org/forums/viewtopic.php?t=2494
